          </div>
      </div>

      <div class="links">
          <div class="link">
              <a class="btn-modheel" href="/services">Book Our Services</a>
          </div>
          <div class="link">
              <a class="btn-modheelo" href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
          <div class="link">
              <a class="btn-modheel" href="/events">Book Our Events</a>
          </div>
      </div>  
    </div>

  <!-- home page for the users -->

  <div class="banner">
    <div class="card-corp">
      <div class="card-titres">
          <h2 class="card-soustitre">Who We Are</h2>
          <p class="modheel-text"> With 15 years of experience in Event Management across France, Tunisia, and Algeria under the name Orients Events, Modheel brings unparalleled expertise to Dubai. We specialize in handling every aspect of your event, from planning and innovative marketing strategies to flawless execution. We are dedicated to transforming your vision into reality, whether it’s a gathering, wedding, birthday celebration, or holiday party. </p>
      </div>
      <video class="video-container2" autoplay muted loop id="mod-video" style="
